field_list.text:
LA Collections Flame-Inspired Ultrasonic Aroma Diffuser – 180ml Mist Humidifier


Product Reminders:

-Maximum tank capacity is 180ml. Do not exceed the water level line to avoid weak misting or potential leakage.
-Use the included Type-C 2A power cable. Other cables may affect misting if they don’t meet the 2A requirement.
-Always use purified water with LA Collections water-based humidifier scents for optimal performance and longer diffuser life.
-Light bubbling or hissing sounds are normal during operation. It’s part of the misting process.

• Aromatherapy Function – Fill with water (do not exceed max line), add a few drops of LA Collections scent, then short-press the mist button to start. Press again to stop.

• Safety Auto Shut-Off – Automatically powers off when water runs out, thanks to a built-in protection sensor.
